tags.name: Monument 77
tags.note: Original monument destroyed during road construction. Relpaced in 1986 with iron post set on edge of roadway. Replacment post presumed to be destroyed because it is not referenced in the 2011 CLSR survey.

tags.bridge:name: Nares Lake Bridge
tags.name: Klondike Highway
tags.note: Bridge replaced in 2019. New bridge was constructed parallel to the old bridge. Distance between centerlines of new and old bridges was about 10 meters. Old bridge has been dismantled.
